description: The user should be able to navigate to linked list page and test the different scenarios in that page

steps.name: Given The user is on Sign In Page of DS Algo Portal
When The user enter valid "Rockstars_Numpy" and "Numpy@Rock123"
Then The user is navigated to homepage
Given The user is on the Linked List page
When The user clicks link from the linked list topics covered list having "Traversal"
Then The user should be navigated to page of "https://dsportalapp.herokuapp.com/linked-list/traversal/"
